a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTgmOJilvbmuSIU49mGkVwk2yS0JcHjv-jfCA&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcTgmOJilvbmuSIU49mGkVwk2yS0JcHjv-jfCA%26usqp%3DCAU&h=03c55f9c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"Mike pence <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三軍紀帥靠你啦，總統中左武肺，其實已經可以直接宣戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T05:41:11.000Z","msg":"個樣鬼鬼地唔知會唔會奶共"},{"pid":"7991091a2387be2a28693f4ac075291a642f7eb2","tid":2226531,"uid":184679,"like":113,"dislike":2,"score":111,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T05:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200930/photo/bkn-20200930080036752-0930_00972_001_01p.jpg?20200930090225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20200930%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200930080036752-0930_00972_001_01p.jpg%3F20200930090225&h=cc3bd4f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78a8a2879fad96e86c9ab726843b5e07caefdb69","tid":2226531,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e6cc177915e6475190313e000f6e0366ca4ec4e7","tid":2226531,"uid":54927,"like":3,"dislike":51,"score":-48,"quote":{"pid":"77b5e5c80d0467c1abc9abddcf69be3806898050","tid":2226531,"uid":197640,"like":111,"dislike":2,"score":109,"quote":{"pid":"9077ba037e050e884836220433c2c37246a51e01","tid":2226531,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T05:36:05.000Z","msg":"美國白宮人員陸續感染新冠肺炎，現在更因為幕僚霍普希克斯（Hope Hicks）確