2956456ac98ad408770afb9cb81889974a7","tid":2226531,"uid":277037,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"e6cc177915e6475190313e000f6e0366ca4ec4e7","tid":2226531,"uid":54927,"like":3,"dislike":51,"score":-48,"quote":{"pid":"77b5e5c80d0467c1abc9abddcf69be3806898050","tid":2226531,"uid":197640,"like":111,"dislike":2,"score":109,"quote":{"pid":"9077ba037e050e884836220433c2c37246a51e01","tid":2226531,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T05:36:05.000Z","msg":"美國白宮人員陸續感染新冠肺炎，現在更因為幕僚霍普希克斯（Hope Hicks）確診，總統川普夫婦在接受病毒檢測後宣布自主隔離。這是否將影響川普參加15日第二次總統候選人電視辯論仍不得而知，但彭博指出，一旦美國正副總統同時因新冠病倒，將引爆一場全面性憲法危機，掀起總統大位爭奪戰。<br />\n<br />\n綜合彭博、BBC報導，身為三軍統帥的美國總統一旦感染新冠肺炎，生病的嚴重程度將會衝擊經濟及地緣政治，特別是川普本人是否喪失行動能力。<br />\n<br />\n地緣政治風險諮詢公司歐亞集團總裁伊恩布雷默（Ian Bremmer）坦言，一旦川普診斷出病情，股市下跌是肯定會有的，但這依據病情有所差距，「如果川普確診被隔離在白宮，但繼續掌管政府，還可以瘋狂發推特，那我想，這對市場的影響微乎其微。」<br />\n<br />\n即便是川普病到連推特都不能發，依據美國憲法第25條修正案，川普可把權力移交給副總統，且在自身狀況恢復後隨即收回權力；依據法律程序，就算是正副總統都已經不在人世，喬治梅森大學法學教授索銘（Ilya Somin）直說，這時候將會由眾院議長接手。<br />\n<br />\n只不過，憲法專家警告，一旦川普和副總統彭斯因為感染新冠肺炎失去行動能力，可能引發新一輪混亂。密西根州立大學法學教授考爾特（Brian Kalt）指出，即使總統這個位子只空閒數小時，對國家來說也都是極其危險的事，若2人都無法履行職責，誰都不能援引憲法第25條修正案。<br />\n<br />\n儘管憲法指示國會制定法律，把眾院議長列為接掌總統職位的人選，但考爾特指出，憲法沒有提供程序來確認總統是否「無能力」履行職責，可能爆發川普、彭斯或他們的代理律師表達自身適合任職的同時，眾院議長宣稱成為代理總統的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n隨著美國大選第二場總統候選人辯論即將於15日在佛州邁阿密登場，川普如今已宣布與夫人梅蘭妮亞自主隔離，這是否影響辯論進行仍不得而知。路透社指出，2人的病毒檢測結果最快當地1日或2日就會有結果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201002/1822796.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20201002%2F1822796.htm&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdArXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=c91eb408\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201002/1822796.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTgmOJilvbmuSIU49mGkVwk2yS0JcHjv-jfCA&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcTgmOJilvbmuSIU49mGkVwk2yS0JcHjv-jfCA%26usqp%3DCAU&h=03c55f9c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"Mike pence <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三軍紀帥靠你啦，總統中左武肺，其實已經可以直接宣戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T05:41:11.000Z","msg":"個樣鬼鬼地唔知會唔會奶共"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T07:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國際視野有幾差先講得出哩句"},{"pid":"b9526fbd0e98e5b13ab1b9013efe0ab1a4966da9","tid":2226531,"uid":307398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T07:22:59.000Z","msg":"Pence<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"014b20d455f013f24f9038713543a0a9cfd5ec13","tid":2226531,"uid":119512,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7991091a2387be2a28693f4ac075291a642f7eb2","tid":2226531,"uid":184679,"like":113,"dislike":2,"score":111,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T05:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200930/photo/bkn-20200930080036752-0930_00972_001_01p.jpg?20200930090225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20200930%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200930080036752-0930_00972_001_01p.jpg%3F20200930090225&h=cc3bd4f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T07:24:00.000Z","msg":"有一軍人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2228961acd8ac7bdbc586883eb1cc53579ec7fad","tid":2226531,"uid":32577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T07:30:46.000Z","msg":"trump 應該扮重病，引中國打台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41bd24bddb78e6fcbb887e810bf5dee9ca08fbc6","tid":2226531,"uid":100581,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7991091a2387be2a28693f4ac075291a642f7eb2","tid":2226531,"uid":184679,"like":113,"dislike":2,"score":111,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T05:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200930/photo/bkn-20200930080036752-0930_00972_001_01p.jpg?20200930090225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20200930%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200930080036752-0930_00972_001_01p.jpg%3F20200930090225&h=cc3bd4f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T07:32:42.000Z","msg":"He is #5 on the list"},{"pid":"df0c2bd30a80b86a901108c185ac7011ec8f6e28","tid":2226531,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ed4a663cd927a63b5ad072451e403c3b222858cb","tid":2226531,"uid":196671,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T07:11:15.000Z","msg":"好玩囉，侵侵同彭斯都收皮，咁跟住第三位係Nancy Pelosi，竟然可能早過野心家希拉莉或假黑人Kamala Harris上到（雖然可能坐三個月就完⋯⋯）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T07:38:48.000Z","msg":"屌 Trump自己講過今年最後可能係配落閪做總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7806667b8545c752e5d8c842a4e3f7fa5ae52917","tid":2226531,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T07:42:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"459a802abdfaf6610f64199287b6ce7840031e1a","tid":2226531,"uid":11506,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7991091a2387be2a28693f4ac075291a642f7eb2","tid":2226531,"uid":184679,"like":113,"dislike":2,"score":111,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T05:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200930/photo/bkn-20200930080036752-0930_00972_001_01p.jpg?20200930090225\" data-th